   3 host/SAMBA@DATADELIKATESSER.SE (aes128-cts-hmac-sha1-96)
   3 host/samba.datadelikatesser.se@DATADELIKATESSER.SE (aes256-cts-hmac-sha1-96)
   3 host/SAMBA@DATADELIKATESSER.SE (aes256-cts-hmac-sha1-96)
